## Quickstart

```bash
docker compose up -d
docker compose logs -f ollama-pull
```

Open `http://localhost`:
1. Register an admin account (first run).
2. Settings → Model Providers → add Ollama (endpoint `http://ollama:11434`).
3. Create an app of type "Chatflow" or "Workflow" → drag and drop nodes.

## Add MCP tool

```bash
perfectrag add mcp tavily --project .
docker compose restart api worker
```

Dify also has its own plugin marketplace inside the UI.

